  "3194510": {
    "name": "Shop Simulator: Pet Shop",
    "steam_appid": 3194510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 <strong>商店模拟器：宠物店</strong> —— 设计你梦想中的宠物店！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸于拥有可爱动物的零售世界，让你的顾客感到满意。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/aa8ddbb66529325f0a301d637e9c7d68.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在电脑上订购新宠物和配件，将动物安置在舒适的沙发或围栏中，让顾客能发现它们。确保库存充足，让每位顾客都能找到心仪的宠物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/57f1b7cee79c4fd90744c470cd6b5a29.poster.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/57f1b7cee79c4fd90744c470cd6b5a29.webm?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/57f1b7cee79c4fd90744c470cd6b5a29.mp4?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/a2d8af36bcc20c087a65c44c8e28ae44.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >顾客带着商品来到收银台，你负责结账并确保一切顺利进行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/2df75e0204971f8eb93ed2d1338a56c3.poster.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/2df75e0204971f8eb93ed2d1338a56c3.webm?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/2df75e0204971f8eb93ed2d1338a56c3.mp4?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/bb9f8dc3b2fdaf1d246a61c2177a49bc.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着游戏进度，你会遇到越来越多可爱的动物朋友，将它们推荐给顾客购买。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/3b847fd4ef09695debb1aa85b8da46da.poster.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/3b847fd4ef09695debb1aa85b8da46da.webm?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/3b847fd4ef09695debb1aa85b8da46da.mp4?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/a85ec6eb71e473835589f3e84a139f60.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你从一个空店开始：可以自由摆放货架、装饰和新的动物朋友。挑选不同的家具，自由布置属于你的店铺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/abe1ca5f6795c4b89f43e3b8d4af020c.poster.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/abe1ca5f6795c4b89f43e3b8d4af020c.webm?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/abe1ca5f6795c4b89f43e3b8d4af020c.mp4?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/dd3f2b912643d741b036b1747b583bc9.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩展你的店铺，雇佣新员工，并实现宠物库存的自动补货。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/7da74d16aef011347907e305b0614b93.poster.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/7da74d16aef011347907e305b0614b93.webm?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/7da74d16aef011347907e305b0614b93.mp4?t=1761307406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/9915d4feefa92ca632e2f798b058362d.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>服务顾客：</strong>扫描、结账，并在必要时开启更多收银台，让更多顾客满意。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心玩法：</strong>在电脑上订购动物和配件，布置你的店铺并赚取收益。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自动化：</strong>利用自动补货系统与员工，提高运营效率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>设计：</strong>用家具和可爱饰品装点你梦想中的店铺。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扩展：</strong>扩建店铺，丰富动物和配件的种类。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多人游戏：</strong>与最多3位好友联机游玩，通过语音聊天协作。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3194510/extras/cc13c6788aa0d0737d1be3d232ca8fe1.avif?t=1761307406\" width=780 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >行动起来吧：开设你自己的宠物店，让所有顾客都满意而归！</p>",
